## Summary of CEL validation behavior

| Rule | Location | Effect |
|---|---|---|
| `!has(oldSelf.tlsMinVersion) && !has(self.tlsMinVersion) \|\| has(oldSelf.tlsMinVersion) && has(self.tlsMinVersion)` | On `IstioCSRConfig` type | Prevents adding the field after creation if it wasn't set initially, and prevents removing it if it was set initially |
| `oldSelf == '' \|\| self == oldSelf` | On `TLSMinVersion` field | Once a non-empty value is persisted, only the same value is accepted on update |
| `Enum:="VersionTLS12";"VersionTLS13"` | On `TLSMinVersion` field | Restricts valid values to exactly `VersionTLS12` and `VersionTLS13` |
